cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this code or methodology, please cite both the journal article and the doctoral thesis below."
type: software
title: "Facebook Reactions as Emotional Indicators: Multi-Method Analysis of COVID-19 News Engagement on Indian Media Platforms"
abstract: >
  This repository contains the full analytical code for the doctoral dissertation
  and associated journal article by Sawood Anwar (University of Urbino Carlo Bo, 2025).
  It employs a mixed-methods approach — combining time-series analysis, BERTopic
  embedding-based topic modelling, LLM-assisted cluster labelling, and lexicon-based
  sentiment analysis — to examine 68,319 Facebook posts from four major English-language
  Indian news outlets (The Times of India, The Hindu, Indian Express, Hindustan Times)
  covering COVID-19 news from March 2020 to March 2022.
